     N TROSY-HSQC spectrum for this complex was rather broad, but superimposed on the broad background were several sharp peaks clustered between 8 and 8.5 p.p.m. in the
     <sup>
      1
     </sup>
     H dimension that disappeared in the TolB Δ
     <sup>
      22−33
     </sup>
     truncation (
     <a>
