       </strong>
       ) Binding of the OM lipoprotein Pal (red) to TolB (grey) favours the state in which the TolA box (green) is sequestered to the TolB surface, thereby diminishing association with domain III of TolA, which we assign as the OFF state for the Tol system. (
       <strong>
